name: Jax.Network
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Jax.Network is anchored to the BTC blockchain that follows the JaxNet protocol and issues scalable, stable, and decentralized JAX coins. We aim at making these coins a universal standard for the quantification of economic value.
